00:25:20,528 --> 00:25:24,886
of course to heat the plasma core,
to drive current non-inductively,

402
00:25:24,886 --> 00:25:27,342
to control the plasma current profile,

403
00:25:27,862 --> 00:25:32,355
and lengthen the ohmic pulse, eventually,

404
00:25:33,287 --> 00:25:35,677
and, as we have seen
in the example of TCV,

