00:28:10,792 --> 00:28:13,151
There is a high degree 
of flexibility, which allows

442
00:28:13,151 --> 00:28:17,761
localized heating and current drive
and therefore a very good degree

443
00:28:17,761 --> 00:28:21,156
of capability of controlling instabilities
